Package: turf
Title: TURF: Total Unduplicated Reach and Frequency
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-06-05
Authors@R: person(
    "Dan", "Yavorsky",
    role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
    email = "dan@gbkcollective.com"
    )
Description: Computes reach and frequency for all combinations of M items chosen
    from J items, retaining the top K combinations ranked by reach. Supports both
    a pure R and an optimized C++ implementation, each with optional parallel
    processing across bundle sizes.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1)
Imports: data.table, Rcpp, foreach, parallel, iterators, doParallel
LinkingTo: Rcpp
VignetteBuilder: knitr, quarto
